26,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"又唔日日唱校歌升校旗"},{"pid":"6637419fd896a7a20f357093af09651b1c255cee","tid":469405,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"國歌唔會唱<br />\n但校歌副歌唱得特別大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3212e400a7231896092f3ac5991965e58b7a8303","tid":469405,"uid":86980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>校長林日豐曾在加拿大念高中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心繫「加」國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71ec61568be1fa9169b73dcf680bb8fa3209159","tid":469405,"uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"香港政府 完全離哂地<br />\n<br />\n以為強逼 學生 唱國歌, 日日洗腦, 就令學生愛國<br />\n事實只會令學生更反感<br />\n<br />\n香港人既價值觀係錢<br />\n<br />\n如果香港政府 想學生愛國, 好簡單...........對住學生講:「你地長大之後奶共, 到時有樓有車有女, 乜都有」<br />\nD學生就好自然「愛國」"},{"pid":"ecb4f3415d142629adaaa295435c44e6769458bb","tid":469405,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"孺子可教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943649ba6039421d8e599168d382ad87e10a3244","tid":469405,"uid":56123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無國何有家，佢係咪調轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先有人，之後幾個人就成一個家<br />\n好多好多個家就成為國<br />\n<br />\n國係由家組成，沒有家，哪有國？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條友on9左狗"},{"pid":"32ebe1337bc7f89b14750f07d76e5e5c2de15dcc","tid":469405,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無國何有家，佢係咪調轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a